WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:15.250 --> 00:00:16.417
From a very young age,

00:00:16.750 --> 00:00:18.410
I became aware of my mother's strength.

00:00:20.017 --> 00:00:25.017
Without my realizing it, she managed to be omnipresent and watch over me at all times.

00:00:26.717 --> 00:00:33.550
She has become part of the way I judge my actions, as she always asked me what I thought of my current or future actions.

00:00:35.117 --> 00:00:42.450
As the years went by, I realized that I am not alone in this, and that mothers remain present in their daughters.

00:00:43.417 --> 00:00:46.650
Now I know that it is a hard,

00:00:47.250 --> 00:00:52.150
painful process, but very effective.

00:00:52.150 --> 00:00:58.450
Motora

00:01:08.650 --> 00:01:14.250
She is probably one of the happiest people you will ever meet.

00:01:16.317 --> 00:01:21.383
She does not need support from anyone to achieve what she wants.

00:01:22.183 --> 00:01:27.583
Correct, stuck up, always perfect.

00:01:28.683 --> 00:01:31.150
She is very noisy.

00:01:31.917 --> 00:01:33.550
She is always willing to help.

00:01:33.550 --> 00:01:35.550
She is always arguing.

00:01:35.817 --> 00:01:37.517
I see her as a kind of man,

00:01:38.083 --> 00:01:42.583
but a very feminine man.

00:01:42.583 --> 00:01:44.580
And very extravagant

00:01:45.683 --> 00:01:48.683
She is liberal in inverted commas

00:01:49.650 --> 00:01:54.250
She is my friend, and I always feel accountable to her.

00:01:54.250 --> 00:01:56.250
She knows that she is the bee's knees.

00:01:56.250 --> 00:01:58.050
She never changes her mind.

00:01:58.050 --> 00:01:59.583
She takes care of me,

00:01:59.583 --> 00:02:01.580
to make sure that I do not eat junk food.

00:02:02.083 --> 00:02:04.750
She would do anything for me.

00:02:04.750 --> 00:02:09.350
She has always tried to change me, but seems to have given up.

00:02:10.083 --> 00:02:14.083
She will say "No!" with such authority, with her finger like this.

00:02:14.083 --> 00:02:17.150
I can hear her finger saying "No" now.

00:02:17.150 --> 00:02:22.483
In any situation, my Mom will always say "Is that correct?"

00:02:22.483 --> 00:02:24.480
Are you doing the right thing?

00:02:24.480 --> 00:02:28.283
I always think of her when I take a decision.

00:02:28.283 --> 00:02:32.317
I know that she will forever be my harshest critic.

00:02:32.317 --> 00:02:35.817
It is as though she could control my feelings.

00:02:36.483 --> 00:02:40.617
Even in the way I raise my daughter, she always wants to be in control.

00:02:40.617 --> 00:02:42.717
She is looking over me, all the time.

00:02:43.317 --> 00:02:47.517
I have always thought that she wants me to do what she did not.

00:02:48.083 --> 00:02:49.510
I want to follow her example:

00:02:49.510 --> 00:02:58.017
"I am the boss round here, and I make the rules because I am your mother. Period."

00:04:12.283 --> 00:04:13.583
Because whether I like it or not,

00:04:13.583 --> 00:04:15.580
I am going to be like my mother!

00:04:15.580 --> 00:04:17.580
Whether I like it or not!

